{"tid":2455626,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"打第二針新冠疫苗注意！翌日宜避粗重工作　","createTime":"2021-03-21T09:15:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T09:58:59.000Z","uid":224066,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0a17f8c9fa1393b8178e5580acdd4ffd95752d86","tid":2455626,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T09:15:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210321/450334768551170048531968.jpeg/POoNQkqOce-3TlkeA9uFskVoGLLnK0w6SS6kHUkupB0?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210321%2F450334768551170048531968.jpeg%2FPOoNQkqOce-3TlkeA9uFskVoGLLnK0w6SS6kHUkupB0%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=db7a7612&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新冠疫苗要接種兩劑才有較高保護力，明日（22日）及後日（23日）分別有官員及市民接種第二劑科興疫苗。有專家稱第二劑疫苗的副作用會較第一劑強，而另一款復必泰疫苗更為明顯，建議請假休息。有醫生稱，科興疫苗副作用較低，只要減少粗重工作，相信大部份人都可以如常生活，而在其診所打針人士接種後不適要請病假，診所開病假紙不會額外收費。至於在接種中心打針的市民，中心並沒有預設開病假紙服務，則可能需要額外求醫。有需要的市民亦宜預先向僱主請假。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210222/440603747672920064012638.jpeg/VYY9ndQdlsRxez2aJSsDM6yRJ_neWfGe_C0qrfwtKq0?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210222%2F440603747672920064012638.jpeg%2FVYY9ndQdlsRxez2aJSsDM6yRJ_neWfGe_C0qrfwtKq0%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=3985b24c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210222/440603750084775936329857.jpeg/_UP0DjdYK8SHMg7rr5Cfde2ukhdx3X7SewrM8XsKzPE?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210222%2F440603750084775936329857.jpeg%2F_UP0DjdYK8SHMg7rr5Cfde2ukhdx3X7SewrM8XsKzPE%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=7f7ea8ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210223/440848465443164160269085.jpeg/3pv9-ljZ82x0gH4-XCa-0JsXNNEyqCy-krTtEZK07RE?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210223%2F440848465443164160269085.jpeg%2F3pv9-ljZ82x0gH4-XCa-0JsXNNEyqCy-krTtEZK07RE%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=3aa6d924&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n市民注射兩劑疫苗才算完成疫苗接種，現時有224,600人接種第一劑科興疫苗。特首林鄭月娥及部份官員早在2月22日接種第一劑科興疫苗，預料明日會注射第二劑；2月23日就有數百名優先群組開打第一針科興疫苗，最快後日會補打第二針。<br />\n<br />\n第二劑疫苗較第一劑更能刺激免疫系統反應，更能產生抗體，同時亦意味副作用可能會較第一針強。本港至少有超過10人接種科興疫苗後，懷疑出現過敏性反應，包括7人出疹、2人有過敏徵狀、2人面癱。"},{"pid":"7d856cb34f425d2bfdc9446d86477dc241d2cc0a","tid":2455626,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T09:16:47.000Z","msg":"香港人最緊要返工<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fv7URZk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffv7URZk.gif&h=ec26ddcb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"048a1d2cf520fa7c86185018b0453403882e1d4d","tid":2455626,"uid":387597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T09:24:25.000Z","msg":"我想講屯門友愛體育館係打科興架....幅圖錯架"},{"pid":"560828273cc60f190d72fe54217cb5ec90479e32","tid":2455626,"uid":349494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"048a1d2cf520fa7c86185018b0453403882e1d4d","tid":2455626,"uid":387597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T09:24:25.000Z","msg":"我想講屯門友愛體育館係打科興架....幅圖錯架"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T09:58:59.000Z","msg":"其實全部都係科興嚟㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}